	measure 'CPI Annual Index (Latest)' = ```
			
			VAR LatestDate =
			    MAX ( 'Annual Dates'[Date] )
			RETURN
			CALCULATE (
			    [CPI Annual Index],
			    'Annual Dates'[Date] = LatestDate
			)
			
			```
